description:
We welcome you to an exciting world where you will take the role of a little dinosaur with a special talent: to make amazing jumps! Your mission is to help this little buddy escape from a world full of exciting challenges.

Get ready for a game full of fun and challenges! Every jump is up to you, and every choice you make brings you closer to the goal. Feel the adrenaline rush as you overcome obstacles and immerse yourself in an experience that will make you jump with excitement.

An exciting platform game full of fun and challenges for all ages, we are waiting for you!
name: Dino Get Out!
